episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

10.title: Swansea and Bridgend

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

11.title: Ashford

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

11.plot: In Ashford, Kent, the first hosts, Francophiles Stephanie and Ian, amaze their guests by living in a tiny version of the Palace of Versailles.

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

13.title: North Devon

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

14.title: Essex and East London

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

15.title: Bournemouth

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

16.title: Kent

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

16.plot: This episode, from Kent, features an egg phobia, a banter battle, an impromptu proposal and a haka. And one contestant puts his foot in it with his own fiancée. Twice.

17.title: Yorkshire

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

18.title: Colchester

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

18.plot: In Colchester, touchy-feely Yvonne and Neil compete against fitness fanatics Darren and Amy, and social worker Tony, who makes uncomplimentary comments about his partner Victoria.

19.title: Rugby

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

19.plot: Party queens Soroya and Jodie serve up an unusual pie that horrifies super-confident Raj in Rugby. And Michael and Caroline search for flaws in Raj and Freddie's 'perfect' relationship.

20.title: East Anglia

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

20.plot: This episode from East Anglia features a performance from unlikely rappers, a confusing spaghetti marrow main course, too many cooks and a fire alarm.

21.title: Sheffield

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

21.plot: In Sheffield, there's non-stop bickering and an evening of romance as car salesman Paul and his partner Sara compete with newlyweds Russell and Shane and kooky duo Janine and Neil.

22.title: East Anglia

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

23.title: The Lake District

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

24.title: Hertfordshire

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

25.title: Wiltshire

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

25.plot: In Wiltshire, Andrew and David host a ritzy affair, but Andrew's celebrity name-dropping fails to impress, and David gets a horrified reaction to his collection of Victorian hair clippings.

27.title: Sheffield and Rotherham

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

29.title: Cornwall

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

30.title: West Yorkshire

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

31.title: Portsmouth and the Isle of Wight

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

32.title: Bradford and Huddersfield

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

33.title: Worthing and Portsmouth

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

35.title: Gloucestershire

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

35.plot: In Gloucestershire, Angela's blender malfunctions and sprays her with gravy, and Paul and Debbie offend their hosts by questioning the intelligence of their beloved Chihuahuas.

36.title: Bristol

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

36.plot: In Bristol, guests are treated to a night of conversation about romantic meetings, outrageous shirts and naked gardening. And some purple potato mash which is more like play-doh.

37.title: Lincolnshire and Yorkshire

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

37.plot: In Lincolnshire and Yorkshire, there's a one-man comedy show, a posh take on some Yorkshire classic dishes, and a big surprise in store for one of the guests.

38.title: Cornwall

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

38.plot: In Cornwall, Sam and Nick share their mutual love of Friesian cows and plans to survive a zombie apocalypse. But can their simple food done well make up for the weirdness.

39.title: Cheltenham

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

39.plot: In Cheltenham, ditzy youngsters Will and Kim keep everyone entertained with their lack of general knowledge and random comments. And can Pasha's Persian rice pudding win the grand.

40.title: Bournemouth

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

41.title: Portsmouth

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

42.title: Glasgow

43.title: Devon

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

44.title: Cumbria

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

45.title: Bognor Regis

46.title: North Wales:

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )

episode of.title: Couples Come Dine with Me (TV Series 2014– )
